{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>現場消息指，事發時豬肉檔與魚檔的職員因事爭執，期間魚檔一名職員持刀襲擊豬肉檔兩名職員。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125394115912011776468132.jpeg/b-O7iKUhK5i_RqdxGAG9peqxnkfhZLh7EGCkIDpgpCA\" alt=\"警員接報到場調查。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>警員接報到場調查。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125395254942765056145397.jpeg/WRwQ7BVItS6RW246xqhqQRtV5JJ6SYF4p2DomI1g6Jg\" alt=\"街市地下遺有一對水鞋及血跡。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>街市地下遺有一對水鞋及血跡。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125395251968872448053894.jpeg/utWwoXrXI2FsflozXVb1hJzsy5Iuza621e0UWP_tFFg\" alt=\"街市地下遺有一對水鞋及血跡。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>街市地下遺有一對水鞋及血跡。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125395248701378560142396.jpeg/v0_JykJJrV3fKVy-Q7su5Ot6okmtGa_uuJw8ZZKcPGU\" alt=\"街市地下六遺有另一對染血的鞋子。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>街市地下六遺有另一對染血的鞋子。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260427/1125395246109167616975286.jpeg/LT-1xWWIYhTV51EfxKHaJgLJcGjnJA0dK0OWOwFDljs\" alt=\"警方到場調查。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>警方到場調查。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20230930/784770304479072256203184.jpeg/D1eKrz00zgOce_C-Z5gjAk43tl-qeHAzxY4HucWOB7k\" alt=\"威爾斯親王醫院。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>威爾斯親王醫院。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-27T03:30:22.878960+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":153,"images":6,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}